rComments: During her lectures, she makes many grammatical errors in French. She is never clear with tests and assignments. However, she is a nice person and is accessible out of class.

She is passionate and shows that she loves her job. However, she is very disorganized. She updates students at the LAST minute, always late when contacting students, doesn't prepare her lectures, arrives late to an appointment, and never clarifies the content on a test. Many were confused with what her tests were going to be on.
